#: .\armor.json
msgid "faraday plate suit"
msgid_plural "faraday plate suits"
msgstr[0] "法拉第板甲套裝"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'faraday plate suit'}
#: .\armor.json
msgid ""
"A suit of Gothic plate armor, complete with gloves, gauntlets, and a barbute"
" helmet.  It has been conductively interconnected, protecting against "
"electricity."
msgstr "一套哥特式板甲，包括手套、護手和帶面罩頭盔。已進行導電互連，可抵禦電擊。"

#: .\armor.json
msgid "leather jumpsuit"
msgid_plural "leather jumpsuits"
msgstr[0] "皮革連體服"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'leather jumpsuit'}
#: .\armor.json
msgid ""
"A short-sleeved jumpsuit made from thick leather.  Provides decent storage "
"and proteciton, and is not very encumbering."
msgstr "一件由厚皮革製成的短袖連體服。提供不錯的存儲空間和防護，且不十分累贅。"

#: .\armor.json
msgid "armored leather jumpsuit"
msgid_plural "armored leather jumpsuits"
msgstr[0] "裝甲皮革連體服"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'armored leather jumpsuit'}
#: .\armor.json
msgid ""
"An armored short-sleeved jumpsuit made from thick leather and metal plates."
"  Cumbersome, but offers excellent protection from harm."
msgstr "一件由厚皮革和金屬板製成的裝甲短袖連體服。笨重，但提供極佳的傷害防護。"

#: .\armor.json
msgid "tire armor"
msgid_plural "tire armors"
msgstr[0] "輪胎護甲"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'tire armor'}
#: .\armor.json
msgid ""
"Makeshift armor made from parts of cut up tires.  Incredibly thick and tough"
" but just as encumbering."
msgstr "由切割輪胎部件製成的臨時護甲。極其厚重堅固，但同樣累贅。"

#: .\armor.json
msgid "hard chest protector"
msgid_plural "hard chest protectors"
msgstr[0] "硬質護胸"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'hard chest protector'}
#: .\armor.json
msgid "A polyurethane chest protector with neoprene backing."
msgstr "一件帶氯丁橡膠背襯的聚氨酯護胸。"

#: .\armor.json
msgid "conductive suit"
msgid_plural "conductive suits"
msgstr[0] "導電服"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'conductive suit'}
#: .\armor.json
msgid ""
"A one piece conductive suit used in linework.  Provides decent physical "
"protection and full protection against electricity.  The hood is designed to"
" fit over a hardhat."
msgstr "一件用於線路作業的一體式導電服。提供良好的物理防護和全面的電擊防護。兜帽設計用於套在安全帽上。"

#: .\armor.json
msgid "floating backpack"
msgid_plural "floating backpacks"
msgstr[0] "懸浮揹包"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'floating backpack'}
#: .\armor.json
msgid ""
"A small backpack with a special rail system designed to reduce the load felt"
" by the wearer when moving up and down.  Good storage for very little "
"encumbrance."
msgstr "一個小型揹包，配有特殊軌道系統，旨在減少穿戴者上下移動時的負重感。以極低的累贅度提供良好的存儲空間。"

#: .\armor.json
msgid "floating rucksack"
msgid_plural "floating rucksacks"
msgstr[0] "懸浮帆布揹包"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'floating rucksack'}
#: .\armor.json
msgid ""
"A huge military rucksack with a special rail system designed to reduce the "
"load felt by the wearer when moving up and down, provides a lot of storage "
"for moderate encumbrance."
msgstr "一個巨大的軍用帆布揹包，配有特殊軌道系統，旨在減少穿戴者上下移動時的負重感，以中等累贅度提供大量存儲空間。"

#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid "XL leather jumpsuit"
msgid_plural "XL leather jumpsuits"
msgstr[0] "XL皮革連體服"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'XL leather jumpsuit'}
#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid ""
"A short-sleeved jumpsuit made from thick leather.  Provides decent storage "
"and proteciton, and is not very encumbering.  This can be worn regardless of"
" your state of mutation"
msgstr "一件由厚皮革製成的短袖連體服。提供不錯的存儲空間和防護，且不十分累贅。無論你的突變狀態如何，均可穿著。"

#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid "XL armored leather jumpsuit"
msgid_plural "XL armored leather jumpsuits"
msgstr[0] "XL裝甲皮革連體服"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'XL armored leather jumpsuit'}
#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid ""
"An armored short-sleeved jumpsuit made from thick leather and metal plates."
"  Cumbersome, but offers excellent protection from harm.  This can be worn "
"regardless of your state of mutation"
msgstr "一件由厚皮革和金屬板製成的裝甲短袖連體服。笨重，但提供極佳的傷害防護。無論你的突變狀態如何，均可穿著。"

#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid "pair of XL leather arm guards"
msgid_plural "pairs of XL leather arm guards"
msgstr[0] "一副XL號皮革護臂"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'pair of XL leather arm guards', 'str_pl': 'pairs
#. of XL leather arm guards'}
#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid ""
"A pair of massive tough leather arm guards.  Fairly light and comfortable."
msgstr "一副巨大而堅韌的皮革護臂。相當輕便舒適。"

#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid "pair of XL leather armor gauntlets"
msgid_plural "pairs of XL leather armor gauntlets"
msgstr[0] "一副XL號皮革護手甲"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'pair of XL leather armor gauntlets', 'str_pl':
#. 'pairs of XL leather armor gauntlets'}
#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid ""
"Heavy and massive fingerless leather gloves.  Very flexible and comfortable."
msgstr "厚重巨大的無指皮革手套。非常靈活舒適。"

#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid "pair of XL leather gloves"
msgid_plural "pairs of XL leather gloves"
msgstr[0] "一副XL號皮革手套"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'pair of XL leather gloves', 'str_pl': 'pairs of
#. XL leather gloves'}
#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid "A massive pair of black leather gloves."
msgstr "一副巨大的黑色皮革手套。"

#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid "XL leather armor helmet"
msgid_plural "XL leather armor helmets"
msgstr[0] "XL號皮革頭盔"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'XL leather armor helmet'}
#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid ""
"A massive and thick leather helmet that provides excellent protection for "
"the head."
msgstr "一頂巨大厚實的皮革頭盔，為頭部提供極佳保護。"

#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid "XL scrap suit"
msgid_plural "XL scrap suits"
msgstr[0] "XL號廢料護甲"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'XL scrap suit'}
#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid ""
"A massive suit of armor made from scraps of metal secured by simple strings;"
" provides decent protection, but the loose collection of plates doesn't make"
" for the most convenient protection."
msgstr "一套由簡單繩索固定的金屬碎片製成的巨大護甲；提供不錯的防護，但鬆散的板甲組合並不便於行動。"

#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid "pair of XL metal arm guards"
msgid_plural "pairs of XL metal arm guards"
msgstr[0] "一副XL號金屬護臂"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'pair of XL metal arm guards', 'str_pl': 'pairs
#. of XL metal arm guards'}
#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid ""
"A massive pair of arm guards hammered out from metal.  Perfect for the Post-"
"Apocalyptic Warrior look."
msgstr "一副由金屬鍛造的巨大護臂。完美契合後末日戰士風格。"

#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid "pair of XL iron greaves"
msgid_plural "pairs of XL iron greaves"
msgstr[0] "一副XL號鐵質護脛"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'pair of XL iron greaves', 'str_pl': 'pairs of XL
#. iron greaves'}
#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid "A massive pair of iron leg guards with a simple leather lining."
msgstr "一副帶有簡易皮革襯裡的巨大鐵質腿部護甲。"

#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid "pair of XL chitinous gauntlets"
msgid_plural "pairs of XL chitinous gauntlets"
msgstr[0] "一副XL號幾丁質護手"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'pair of XL chitinous gauntlets', 'str_pl':
#. 'pairs of XL chitinous gauntlets'}
#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid ""
"Massive gauntlets made from the exoskeletons of insects.  Very light and "
"durable."
msgstr "由昆蟲外骨骼製成的巨大護手。非常輕便耐用。"

#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid "pair of XL biosilicified chitin gauntlets"
msgid_plural "pairs of XL biosilicified chitin gauntlets"
msgstr[0] "一副XL號生物硅化幾丁質護手"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'pair of XL biosilicified chitin gauntlets',
#. 'str_pl': 'pairs of XL biosilicified chitin gauntlets'}
#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid ""
"Massive gauntlets crafted from the carefully cleaned and pruned "
"biosilicified exoskeletons of acidic ants.  Acid-resistant and very durable."
msgstr "由精心清潔修剪的酸性螞蟻生物硅化外骨骼製成的巨大護手。耐酸且非常耐用。"

#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid "XL chitinous helmet"
msgid_plural "XL chitinous helmets"
msgstr[0] "XL號幾丁質頭盔"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'XL chitinous helmet'}
#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid ""
"A massive helmet made from the exoskeletons of insects.  Covers the entire "
"head; very light and durable."
msgstr "一頂由昆蟲外骨骼製成的巨大頭盔。覆蓋整個頭部；非常輕便耐用。"

#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid "XL biosilicified chitin helmet"
msgid_plural "XL biosilicified chitin helmets"
msgstr[0] "XL號生物硅化幾丁質頭盔"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'XL biosilicified chitin helmet'}
#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid ""
"A massive helmet crafted from the carefully cleaned and pruned biosilicified"
" exoskeletons of acidic ants.  Covers the entire head; acid-resistant and "
"very durable."
msgstr "一頂由精心清潔修剪的酸性螞蟻生物硅化外骨骼製成的巨大頭盔。覆蓋整個頭部；耐酸且非常耐用。"

#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid "pair of XL chitin arm guards"
msgid_plural "pairs of XL chitin arm guards"
msgstr[0] "一副XL號幾丁質護臂"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'pair of XL chitin arm guards', 'str_pl': 'pairs
#. of XL chitin arm guards'}
#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid ""
"A pair of massive arm guards made from the exoskeletons of insects.  Light "
"and durable."
msgstr "一副由昆蟲外骨骼製成的巨大護臂。輕便耐用。"

#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid "pair of XL biosilicified chitin arm guards"
msgid_plural "pairs of XL biosilicified chitin arm guards"
msgstr[0] "一副XL號生物硅化幾丁質護臂"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'pair of XL biosilicified chitin arm guards',
#. 'str_pl': 'pairs of XL biosilicified chitin arm guards'}
#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid ""
"A pair of massive arm guards crafted from the carefully cleaned and pruned "
"biosilicified exoskeletons of acidic ants.  Acid-resistant and very durable."
msgstr "一副由精心清潔修剪的酸性螞蟻生物硅化外骨骼製成的巨大護臂。耐酸且非常耐用。"

#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid "XL chitinous armor"
msgid_plural "XL chitinous armors"
msgstr[0] "XL號幾丁質護甲"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'XL chitinous armor'}
#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid ""
"Massive leg and body armor made from the exoskeletons of insects.  Light and"
" durable."
msgstr "由昆蟲外骨骼製成的巨大腿部和軀幹護甲。輕便耐用。"

#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid "XL biosilicified chitin armor"
msgid_plural "XL biosilicified chitin armors"
msgstr[0] "XL號生物硅化幾丁質護甲"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'XL biosilicified chitin armor'}
#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid ""
"Massive leg and body armor crafted from the carefully cleaned and pruned "
"biosilicified exoskeletons of acidic ants.  Acid-resistant and very durable."
msgstr "由精心清潔修剪的酸性螞蟻生物硅化外骨骼製成的巨大腿部和軀幹護甲。耐酸且非常耐用。"

#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid "pair of XL flame-resistant gloves"
msgid_plural "pairs of XL flame-resistant gloves"
msgstr[0] "一雙XL號阻燃手套"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'pair of XL flame-resistant gloves', 'str_pl':
#. 'pairs of XL flame-resistant gloves'}
#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid ""
"A massive, snug fitting pair of gloves made from thin and lightweight Nomex "
"fire-resistant fabric.  Tough yet breathable, they are light and comfortable"
" to wear under clothing."
msgstr "一副由輕薄諾梅克斯阻燃面料製成的大號緊貼合手套。堅韌且透氣，輕便舒適，適合穿在衣物內層。"

#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid "XL flame-resistant hood"
msgid_plural "XL flame-resistant hoods"
msgstr[0] "XL號阻燃頭罩"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'XL flame-resistant hood'}
#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid ""
"A massive, snug fitting garment that protects your head and neck, made from "
"lightweight Nomex fire-resistant fabric.  Tough yet breathable, it is light "
"and comfortable to wear under clothing."
msgstr "一件由輕質諾梅克斯阻燃面料製成的大號緊貼合服裝，可保護頭部和頸部。堅韌且透氣，輕便舒適，適合穿在衣物內層。"

#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid "pair of XL flame-resistant socks"
msgid_plural "pairs of XL flame-resistant socks"
msgstr[0] "一雙XL號阻燃襪子"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'pair of XL flame-resistant socks', 'str_pl':
#. 'pairs of XL flame-resistant socks'}
#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid ""
"A massive, snug fitting pair of stockings made from thin and lightweight "
"Nomex fire-resistant fabric.  Tough yet breathable, they are light and "
"comfortable to wear under clothing."
msgstr "一雙由輕薄諾梅克斯阻燃面料製成的大號緊貼合長襪。堅韌且透氣，輕便舒適，適合穿在衣物內層。"

#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid "flame-resistant suit"
msgid_plural "flame-resistant suits"
msgstr[0] "阻燃套裝"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'flame-resistant suit'}
#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid ""
"A massive, snug body suit made from thin and lightweight Nomex fire-"
"resistant fabric.  Tough yet breathable, it is light and comfortable to wear"
" under clothing."
msgstr "一件由輕薄諾梅克斯阻燃面料製成的大號緊貼合連體衣。堅韌且透氣，輕便舒適，適合穿在衣物內層。"

#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid "XL sleeveless trenchcoat"
msgid_plural "XL sleeveless trenchcoats"
msgstr[0] "XL號無袖風衣"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'XL sleeveless trenchcoat'}
#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid ""
"A massive cotton trenchcoat that leaves your arms unencumbered.  Has plenty "
"of storage space due to its many pockets."
msgstr "一件大號棉質風衣，解放你的雙臂。因多個口袋而擁有充足的存儲空間。"

#: .\armor_xl.json
