msgstr "一件大號無袖全長皮風衣，解放你的雙臂。因多個口袋而擁有充足的存儲空間。"

#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid "XL cargo pants"
msgid_plural "XL cargo pants"
msgstr[0] "XL號工裝褲"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'XL cargo pants', 'str_pl': 'XL cargo pants'}
#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid "A massive pair of pants lined with pockets, offering lots of storage."
msgstr "一條大號內襯多個口袋的褲子，提供大量存儲空間。"

#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid "XL cargo shorts"
msgid_plural "XL cargo shorts"
msgstr[0] "XL號工裝短褲"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'XL cargo shorts', 'str_pl': 'XL cargo shorts'}
#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid "A massive pair of shorts lined with pockets, offering decent storage."
msgstr "一條大號內襯多個口袋的短褲，提供不錯的存儲空間。"

#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid "XL plate armor"
msgid_plural "XL plate armors"
msgstr[0] "XL號板甲"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'XL plate armor'}
#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid "A massive suit of Gothic plate armor."
msgstr "一套大號哥特式板甲。"

#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid "pair of XL armored gauntlets"
msgid_plural "pairs of XL armored gauntlets"
msgstr[0] "一副XL號裝甲護手"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'pair of XL armored gauntlets', 'str_pl': 'pairs
#. of XL armored gauntlets'}
#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid "An extremely heavy set of massive armor-plated leather gloves."
msgstr "一副極其沉重的巨大裝甲皮革手套。"

#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid "XL barbute helm"
msgid_plural "XL barbute helms"
msgstr[0] "XL號桶盔"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'XL barbute helm'}
#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid ""
"A massive medieval helmet that provides excellent protection for the head, "
"with a Y shaped opening for the face."
msgstr "一頂巨大的中世紀頭盔，為頭部提供極佳保護，面部有Y形開口。"

#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid "XL great helm"
msgid_plural "XL great helms"
msgstr[0] "XL號大盔"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'XL great helm'}
#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid ""
"A massive medieval helmet that provides excellent protection to the entire "
"head, at the cost of great encumbrance."
msgstr "一頂巨大的中世紀頭盔，為整個頭部提供極佳保護，但代價是極為笨重。"

#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid "XL O-yoroi"
msgid_plural "XL O-yorois"
msgstr[0] "XL號大鎧"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'XL O-yoroi'}
#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid "A massive ornamental suit of Japanese samurai armor."
msgstr "一套巨大的裝飾性日本武士鎧甲。"

#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid "XL kabuto"
msgid_plural "XL kabutos"
msgstr[0] "XL號兜"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'XL kabuto'}
#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid ""
"A massive medieval Japanese helmet with a scowling facemask that provides "
"excellent protection to the entire head and face."
msgstr "一頂巨大的中世紀日本頭盔，配有怒容面甲，為整個頭部和麵部提供極佳保護。"

#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid "XL faraday plate suit"
msgid_plural "XL faraday plate suits"
msgstr[0] "XL號法拉第板甲套裝"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'XL faraday plate suit'}
#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid ""
"A massive suit of Gothic plate armor, complete with boots, gauntlets, and a "
"barbute helmet.  It has been conductively interconnected, protecting against"
" electricity."
msgstr "一套巨大的哥特式板甲，包括靴子、護手和一頂桶盔。它已導電互連，可抵禦電擊。"

#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid "pair of XL steel arm guards"
msgid_plural "pairs of XL steel arm guards"
msgstr[0] "一副XL號鋼製臂甲"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'pair of XL steel arm guards', 'str_pl': 'pairs
#. of XL steel arm guards'}
#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid ""
"A massive full assembly of medieval arm protection.  Rerebraces, couters, "
"and vambraces, with leather straps to secure each piece and connect it as "
"part of a set."
msgstr "一套巨大的中世紀手臂防護全組件。包括上臂甲、肘甲和前臂甲，配有皮帶以固定每個部件並連接成一套。"

#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid "XL cuirass"
msgid_plural "XL cuirasses"
msgstr[0] "XL號胸甲"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'XL cuirass', 'str_pl': 'XL cuirasses'}
#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid ""
"A massive steel breastplate, and a vital part of plate armor.  Even as full "
"armor went into decline, cuirasses remained in use among cavalry in Europe."
msgstr "一件巨大的鋼製胸甲，是板甲的關鍵部分。即使全身甲逐漸衰落，胸甲在歐洲騎兵中仍繼續使用。"

#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid "pair of XL steel leg guards"
msgid_plural "pairs of XL steel leg guards"
msgstr[0] "一副XL號鋼製腿甲"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'pair of XL steel leg guards', 'str_pl': 'pairs
#. of XL steel leg guards'}
#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid ""
"A masive full assembly of medieval leg protection.  Cuisses, poleyns, and "
"greaves, with leather straps to secure each piece and connect it as part of "
"a set."
msgstr "一套巨大的中世紀腿部防護全組件。包括大腿甲、膝甲和小腿甲，配有皮帶以固定每個部件並連接成一套。"

#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid "XL faraday chainmail suit"
msgid_plural "XL faraday chainmail suits"
msgstr[0] "XL號法拉第鎖子甲套裝"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'XL faraday chainmail suit'}
#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid ""
"A massive, fully customized chainmail suit.  The coif, shirt, arms, and "
"leggings have been modified with leather straps to deal with uneven weight "
"distribution and to allow them to be used separately.  It has been combined "
"with a set of armored boots and gauntlets and conductively interconnected, "
"protecting against electricity."
msgstr ""
"一套巨大的全定製鎖子甲套裝。頭巾、襯衫、手臂和腿甲已用皮帶改裝，以應對重量分佈不均並允許單獨使用。它與一套裝甲靴和護手結合，並導電互連，可抵禦電擊。"

#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid "XL chainmail armor"
msgid_plural "XL chainmail armors"
msgstr[0] "XL號鎖子甲"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'XL chainmail armor'}
#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid ""
"A massive fully customized chainmail suit.  The coif, shirt, arms, and "
"leggings have been modified with leather straps to deal with uneven weight "
"distribution and to allow them to be used separately."
msgstr "一套巨大的全定製鎖子甲套裝。頭巾、襯衫、手臂和腿甲已用皮帶改裝，以應對重量分佈不均並允許單獨使用。"

#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid "pair of XL chainmail sleeves"
msgid_plural "pairs of XL chainmail sleeves"
msgstr[0] "一副XL號鎖子甲袖套"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'pair of XL chainmail sleeves', 'str_pl': 'pairs
#. of XL chainmail sleeves'}
#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid ""
"Massive customized chainmail arms.  Each sleeve has leather straps to "
"connect them with each other.  The lack of fingers makes them less "
"cumbersome and allows them to be used with gloves."
msgstr "巨大的定製鎖子甲手臂部件。每個袖套都有皮帶相互連接。缺少手指的設計使其不那麼笨重，並可與手套搭配使用。"

#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid "XL chainmail coif"
msgid_plural "XL chainmail coifs"
msgstr[0] "XL號鎖子甲頭巾"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'XL chainmail coif'}
#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid ""
"A massive customized chainmail hood.  Can be worn comfortably under helmets."
msgstr "一頂巨大的定製鎖子甲頭巾。可舒適地戴在頭盔下。"

#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid "XL chainmail leggings"
msgid_plural "pairs of XL chainmail leggings"
msgstr[0] "XL號鎖子甲腿套"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'XL chainmail leggings', 'str_pl': 'pairs of XL
#. chainmail leggings'}
#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid ""
"Massive customized chainmail legs.  Their leather straps keep everything in "
"place, and the lack of toes and heels allows them to work perfectly well "
"with footwear."
msgstr "巨大的定製鎖子甲腿部部件。其皮帶確保一切固定到位，缺少腳趾和腳跟的設計使其與鞋類完美搭配。"

#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid "chainmail vest"
msgid_plural "chainmail vests"
msgstr[0] "鎖子甲背心"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'chainmail vest'}
#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid ""
"A customized chainmail vest.  It's a sleeveless piece of chainmail with "
"small leather straps designed to better distribute the weight."
msgstr "一件定製的鎖子甲背心。這是一件無袖鎖子甲，配有小型皮帶以更好地分散重量。"

#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid "pair of XL boots"
msgid_plural "pairs of XL boots"
msgstr[0] "一雙XL碼靴子"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'pair of XL boots', 'str_pl': 'pairs of XL
#. boots'}
#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid "Massive leather boots.  Very durable."
msgstr "巨大的皮靴。非常耐用。"

#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid "pair of XL leather armor boots"
msgid_plural "pairs of XL leather armor boots"
msgstr[0] "一雙XL碼皮甲靴"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'pair of XL leather armor boots', 'str_pl':
#. 'pairs of XL leather armor boots'}
#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid ""
"Massive leather boots made specifically to protect the feet.  Light and "
"tough."
msgstr "專為保護雙腳而制的巨大皮靴。輕便且堅韌。"

#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid "pair of XL armored boots"
msgid_plural "pairs of XL armored boots"
msgstr[0] "一雙XL碼裝甲靴"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'pair of XL armored boots', 'str_pl': 'pairs of
#. XL armored boots'}
#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid "An extremely heavy set of massive armor plated boots."
msgstr "一套極其沉重的巨大裝甲板靴。"

#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid "pair of XL chitinous boots"
msgid_plural "pairs of XL chitinous boots"
msgstr[0] "一雙XL碼幾丁質靴"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'pair of XL chitinous boots', 'str_pl': 'pairs of
#. XL chitinous boots'}
#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid ""
"Massive boots made from the exoskeletons of insects.  Light and durable."
msgstr "由昆蟲外骨骼製成的巨大靴子。輕便且耐用。"

#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid "pair of XL biosilicified chitin boots"
msgid_plural "pairs of XL biosilicified chitin boots"
msgstr[0] "一雙XL碼生物硅化幾丁質靴"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'pair of XL biosilicified chitin boots',
#. 'str_pl': 'pairs of XL biosilicified chitin boots'}
#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid ""
"Massive boots crafted from carefully cleaned and pruned biosilicified "
"exoskeletons of acidic ants.  Acid-resistant and very durable."
msgstr "由精心清潔和修剪過的酸性螞蟻生物硅化外骨骼製成的巨大靴子。耐酸且非常耐用。"

#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid "XL backpack"
msgid_plural "XL backpacks"
msgstr[0] "XL碼揹包"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'XL backpack'}
#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid "A large backpack.  Good storage for a little encumbrance."
msgstr "一個大揹包。提供良好的存儲空間，僅帶來輕微負擔。"

#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid "XL leather backpack"
msgid_plural "XL leather backpacks"
msgstr[0] "XL碼皮革揹包"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'XL leather backpack'}
#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid "A large leather backpack.  Good storage for a little encumbrance."
msgstr "一個大型皮革揹包。提供良好的存儲空間，僅帶來輕微負擔。"

#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid "XL duffel bag"
msgid_plural "XL duffel bags"
msgstr[0] "XL碼行李袋"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'XL duffel bag'}
#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid ""
"A massive duffel bag.  Provides plenty of storage, but is severely "
"encumbering."
msgstr "一個巨大的行李袋。提供充足的存儲空間，但會造成嚴重負擔。"

#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid "XL tool belt"
msgid_plural "XL tool belts"
msgstr[0] "XL碼工具腰帶"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'XL tool belt'}
#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid ""
"A massive belt with pockets and four small belt loops.  Widely used by "
"handymen and electricians if handymen and electricians were bears."
msgstr "一條帶有口袋和四個小腰帶環的巨大腰帶。如果勤雜工和電工是熊的話，他們會廣泛使用它。"

#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid "XL chest rig"
msgid_plural "XL chest rigs"
msgstr[0] "XL碼胸掛"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'XL chest rig'}
#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid ""
"A massive vest covered in webbing, pockets and straps.  This variety is "
"favored by the military, as it is capable of holding four magazines close at"
" hand."
msgstr "一件覆蓋著織帶、口袋和帶子的巨大背心。這種款式深受軍方青睞，因為它能容納四個彈匣，便於取用。"

#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid "pair of XL drop leg pouches"
msgid_plural "pairs of XL drop leg pouches"
msgstr[0] "一雙XL碼腿掛包"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'pair of XL drop leg pouches', 'str_pl': 'pairs
#. of XL drop leg pouches'}
#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid ""
"A massive set of pouches that can be worn on the thighs using buckled "
"straps.  This variety is favored by the military."
msgstr "一套巨大的包袋，可通過帶扣綁帶佩戴在大腿上。這種款式深受軍方青睞。"

#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid "XL tire armor"
msgid_plural "XL tire armors"
msgstr[0] "XL碼輪胎裝甲"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'XL tire armor'}
#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid ""
"Massive makeshift armor made from parts of cut up tires.  Incredibly thick "
"and tough but just as encumbering."
msgstr "由切割輪胎部件製成的巨大臨時裝甲。極其厚重堅韌，但同樣會造成負擔。"

#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid "XL hard chest protector"
msgid_plural "XL hard chest protectors"
msgstr[0] "XL碼硬質胸甲"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'XL hard chest protector'}
#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid ""
"A polyurethane chest protector with neoprene backing.  This can be worn "
"regardless of your state of mutation"
msgstr "一件帶有氯丁橡膠背襯的聚氨酯胸甲。無論你的突變狀態如何，都可以穿戴。"

#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid "XL conductive suit"
msgid_plural "XL conductive suits"
msgstr[0] "XL碼導電服"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'XL conductive suit'}
#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid ""
"A one piece conductive suit used in linework.  Provides decent physical "
"protection and full protection against electricity.  The hood is designed to"
" fit over a hardhat.  This can be worn regardless of your state of mutation"
msgstr "一件用於線路作業的一體式導電服。提供良好的物理防護和全面的電擊防護。兜帽設計用於套在安全帽上。無論你的突變狀態如何，都可以穿戴。"

#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid "XL floating backpack"
msgid_plural "XL floating backpacks"
msgstr[0] "XL碼懸浮揹包"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'XL floating backpack'}
#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid ""
"A small backpack with a special rail system designed to reduce the load felt"
" by the wearer when moving up and down.  Good storage for very little "
"encumbrance.  This can be worn regardless of your state of mutation"
msgstr "一個小型揹包，配有特殊軌道系統，旨在減少穿戴者上下移動時感受到的負荷。提供良好的存儲空間，負擔極小。無論你的突變狀態如何，都可以穿戴。"

#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid "XL floating rucksack"
msgid_plural "XL floating rucksacks"
msgstr[0] "XL懸浮揹包"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'XL floating rucksack'}
#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid ""
"A huge military rucksack with a special rail system designed to reduce the "
"load felt by the wearer when moving up and down, provides a lot of storage "
"for moderate encumbrance.  This can be worn regardless of your state of "
"mutation"
msgstr "一款巨大的軍用揹包，配有特殊導軌系統，旨在減輕穿戴者上下移動時的負重感，提供大量存儲空間且負重適中。無論你的突變狀態如何，均可穿戴。"

#: .\modinfo.json
msgid "More Armors"
msgstr "更多護甲"

#. ~ Description for More Armors
#: .\modinfo.json
msgid ""
"Adds more armors with recipes. Mainly XL versions for mutated characters, "
"but there are a few new ones too."
msgstr "添加更多帶配方的護甲。主要為突變角色設計的XL版本，但也包含一些全新護甲。"
